ed="T" n="0887c01"/><persName key="A010449">釋普勝</persName>，姓<name>張氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000003679"><placeName>深州</placeName><placeName>陸澤</placeName></placeName>人也。幼歲情愛媮<lb
ed="T" n="0887c02"/>薄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2329"/>，俄決志趨<placeName key="PL000000005362"><placeName>五臺山</placeName><placeName>華嚴寺</placeName></placeName>，師事<persName key="A013779">超化大<lb
ed="T" n="0887c03"/>師</persName>。或問之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010449">子</ref>胡以越山踰域而求出家？<lb
ed="T" n="0887c04"/>彼<placeName key="PL000000003678">饒陽</placeName>者，豈無仁祠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1894"/>哲匠乎？」<persName key="A010449">勝</persName>對曰：「附神<lb
ed="T" n="0887c05"/>驥可以日千里矣。某知<persName key="A002144">妙吉</persName>淨剎感徵膠<lb
ed="T" n="0887c06"/>戾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1241"/>，令<ref type="person" target="#A010449">我</ref>小凡速成果證，可不是乎？」眾<anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz13"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>耹</sic><corr>聆</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz13"/>斯<lb
ed="T" n="0887c07"/>說，曰：「任氣小兒，有此高識，我曹俱弗如也。」<lb
ed="T" n="0887c08"/><persName key="A010449">勝</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010449">某</ref>非衽金革死而不厭之徒也<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1244"/>，願入<lb
ed="T" n="0887c09"/>慈門<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2330"/>而思利物耳。」迨乎受具，南臨<placeName key="PL000000004355">潞府</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0887c10"/>講通《上生經》<ptr target="#n772"/>矣。聞<persName key="A042600">崇法<roleName>大師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n3503"/>傳《唯識論》<ptr target="#n2051"/>，盛<lb
ed="T" n="0887c11"/>化<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛都</placeName>，往從學焉。凡百章疏，經目便識之。<lb
ed="T" n="0887c12"/>不幾稔閒，習通精贍。<persName key="A010449">勝</persName>所傳者<placeName key="PL000000002513">中山</placeName><persName key="A009888">貞辯</persName>《鈔》<ptr target="#n3504"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0887c13"/>講多誤失所然，昌言曰：「繁略不均，解判非<lb
ed="T" n="0887c14"/>當。」乃刪多補少為四卷，行于世。<persName key="A003883">太祖神德<lb
ed="T" n="0887c15"/>皇帝</persName>賜紫衣，師號曰<persName key="A010449">宣教</persName>也。以<date key="j20788482078848" when-iso="+0979-08-04"><name>太平興國</name><lb
ed="T" n="0887c16"/>四年秋七月四日</date>示疾，終于<placeName key="PL000000023653">淨土院</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0887sgsz15"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>亨</sic><corr>享</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0887sgsz15"/>壽<lb
ed="T" n="0887c17"/>六十三，坐四十三夏。門人等收舍利葬于<lb
ed="T" n="0887c18"/><placeName key="PL000000023547"><placeName>龍門山</placeName><placeName>寶應寺</placeName></placeName>西阜，建塔旌表之。</p>
